                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="481611" author="JIRAUSER18021" created="Wed, 17 Dec 2025 13:34:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=acedeyn&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;acedeyn&quot;&gt;acedeyn&lt;/a&gt; thank you for pointing out this workaround!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="481608" author="JIRAUSER19803" created="Wed, 17 Dec 2025 13:16:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I hit this issue but it&apos;s not really a &lt;tt&gt;make install&lt;/tt&gt; issue but a &lt;tt&gt;configure&lt;/tt&gt; issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I dumbly compiled and installed e2fsprogs with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# ./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# ls -l /usr/lib64/libext2fs.*
&lt;/span&gt;-r--r--r--. 1 root root 5186690 Dec 17 13:11 /usr/lib64/libext2fs.a
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The result is that only libext2fs.a was installed in /usr/lib64.&lt;br/&gt;
To solve the issue, you must add &lt;tt&gt;--enable-elf-shlibs&lt;/tt&gt; on configure command line&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# ./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-elf-shlibs  &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# ls -l /usr/lib64/libext2fs.*
&lt;/span&gt;-r--r--r--. 1 root root 5186690 Dec 17 13:13 /usr/lib64/libext2fs.a
lrwxrwxrwx. 1 root root      14 Dec 17 13:13 /usr/lib64/libext2fs.so -&amp;gt; libext2fs.so.2
lrwxrwxrwx. 1 root root      16 Dec 17 13:13 /usr/lib64/libext2fs.so.2 -&amp;gt; libext2fs.so.2.4
-rwxr-xr-x. 1 root root 2717616 Dec 17 13:13 /usr/lib64/libext2fs.so.2.4
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="349404" author="pjones" created="Wed, 12 Oct 2022 17:14:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jian&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you please investigate?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
